{"tha-ap417:0.1":"Therapadana ","tha-ap417:0.2":"Bhaddalivagga ","tha-ap417:0.3":"5 Nagapallavattheraapadana ","tha-ap417:1.1":"“Nagare bandhumatiya, ","tha-ap417:1.2":"rajuyyane vasamaham; ","tha-ap417:1.3":"Mama assamasamanta, ","tha-ap417:1.4":"nisidi lokanayako. ","tha-ap417:2.1":"Nagapallavamadaya, ","tha-ap417:2.2":"buddhassa abhiropayim; ","tha-ap417:2.3":"Pasannacitto sumano, ","tha-ap417:2.4":"sugatam abhivadayim. ","tha-ap417:3.1":"Ekanavutito kappe, ","tha-ap417:3.2":"yam pallavamapujayim; ","tha-ap417:3.3":"Duggatim nabhijanami, ","tha-ap417:3.4":"buddhapujayidam phalam. ","tha-ap417:4.1":"Kilesa jhapita mayham, ","tha-ap417:4.2":"…pe… ","tha-ap417:4.3":"viharami anasavo. ","tha-ap417:5.1":"Svagatam vata me asi, ","tha-ap417:5.2":"…pe… ","tha-ap417:5.3":"katam buddhassa sasanam. ","tha-ap417:6.1":"Patisambhida catasso, ","tha-ap417:6.2":"…pe… ","tha-ap417:6.3":"katam buddhassa sasanam”. ","tha-ap417:7.1":"Ittham sudam ayasma nagapallavo thero ima gathayo abhasitthati. ","tha-ap417:8.1":"Nagapallavattherassapadanam pancamam. "}